  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Moviprep or Phosphoral is the best method
      of bowel preparation before colonoscopy - seen by the patients and by the endoscopist.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
